Safety-ScoreExpl: The Safety Score is computed by Beefy‚Äôs developers when assessing a vault. No score can capture risk levels perfectly, but Beefy finds it a useful gauge in making decisions. The Safety Score ranks a vault from 0 to 10, worst to best.

Each vault also has a panic facility to pause activity to protect user funds at short notice if the need arises, or even suspicious activity is identified.

beFTM-description: beFTM simply means Beefy Escrowed Fantom. The token is pegged to FTM and can be staked on the Beefy platform and farms on major DEXs. beFTM gives stakers access to maximized validator rewards that typically aren‚Äôt available to the individual investor without locking FTM for 1 year.
Mint-Reminder: {{token1}} is minted at a 1:1 ratio with {{token2}}. If {{token1}}'s price is under peg when a user attempts to mint, {{token1}} will instead be purchased at the better market rate.
Mint-Content: Lock your {{token2}} to get {{token1}}. Each {{token1}} is backed by 1 {{token2}}.
Mint-Content-Burnable: Mint {{token1}} by depositing {{token2}}. {{token1}} can be staked into a Beefy Vault. {{token1}} can be exchanged back to {{token2}} when there is a supply in our reserves.
Mint-Content-Burnable-Earnings: Mint {{token1}} by depositing {{token2}}. {{token1}} can be staked into a Beefy Vault or Earnings Pool. {{token1}} can be exchanged back to {{token2}} when there is a supply in our reserves.
Burn-Content: Burn {{token1}} for {{token2}} when there is {{token2}} in reserves. Our reserves increase when users deposit {{token2}} for {{token1}}.
beJOE-description: beJOE is Beefy Staked JOE. The token is pegged to JOE and can be staked on the Beefy platform to earn JOE or more beJOE. beJOE gives stakers access to 5% of all Beefy Trader Joe Boosted farm rewards. You can burn beJOE for JOE if there is available JOE reserves.
beQI-description: beQI is Beefy Staked QI. The token is pegged to QI and can be staked on the Beefy platform to earn QI or more beQI. beQI gives stakers access to max lock rewards of staking QI for eQI. You can burn beQI for QI if there is available QI reserves.

InfoCard-binSPIRIT-Title: Vote on SPIRIT Emissions with binSPIRIT
InfoCard-binSPIRIT-Work-Text: SpiritSwap‚Äôs inSPIRIT governance token uses a vote locking model. binSPIRIT is a wrapped version of 4-year-locked inSPIRIT. inSPIRIT & binSPIRIT holders receive voting power, participation rewards, and boosted farming rewards. binSPIRIT holders can vote weekly on the gauges to receive SPIRIT emission allocation.
InfoCard-binSPIRIT-Bribes-Title: Use Beefy‚Äôs Voting Power to Earn Bribes
InfoCard-binSPIRIT-Bribes-Text: 50% of Beefy‚Äôs voting rights from locking SPIRIT are given to binSPIRIT holders. Beefy distributes these rights to binSPIRIT users to vote weekly via Snapshot. There is an open bribe environment for projects to bribe binSPIRIT holders for their voting power. Voters will receive bribes via an airdrop generated from the voting history.
